{"tid":1229013,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"未瞓嘅，失眠嘅，送一首歌俾大家","createTime":"2019-06-15T19:50:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T19:53:02.000Z","uid":197024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1f318349ea9db3937cef09e08a77a910552fd6b1","tid":1229013,"uid":197024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T19:50:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Z8WlLPEJp0U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZ8WlLPEJp0U&d=GKwB35BxKisFbiFxv4h%2FhtVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=8b5a4cb8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Z8WlLPEJp0U</a><br />\n<br />\n今晚對我，對好多巴絲嚟講，係一個好長嘅夜晚。<br />\n<br />\n好攰，好心痛，無力感好重。<br />\n<br />\n尤其是一班廢中，廢老毫無營養，冷血，自私嘅言論，我相信你我呢幾日都聽唔少。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但係</span>，唔好忘記呢度有成班連登仔，同埋7份之1嘅香港人做後盾。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，一個都不能少。<br />\n連登仔，更加一個都不能少。<br />\n<br />\n如果其他巴絲有乜嘢歌想今晚同大家share，不如留cm分享。"},{"pid":"b733066fc23c978465400c2b8ba041335421daa2","tid":1229013,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T19:53:02.000Z","msg":"好彩唔係sing Hallelujah <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}